{"tid":359482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全力支持】今日開始只會幫襯A1麵包店","createTime":"2017-08-14T14:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T04:00:37.000Z","uid":36551,"like":58,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a112e80fb6dd1d234bbfd3f5e9c86db0fe1ade0","tid":359482,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:00:40.000Z","msg":"A-1麵包店5次違規派膠袋罪成 首間大型連鎖店遭刑事檢控<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0814 18:06<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170814/large/1502705679_cbcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170814%2Flarge%2F1502705679_cbcf.jpg&h=e39745c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大型連鎖麵包店A-1 Bakery被發現在沒徵費下向顧客提供膠袋，今遭環保署刑事檢控並被罰款5,000元。<br />\n<br />\n自2015年4月全面實施膠袋徵費，今為首次有大型連鎖零售商因違反《產品環保責任條例》被刑事檢控。環保署透露，去年三月抽查零售點時發現A-1 Bakery的國際機場分店，在出售非冷凍樽裝水時未有依例向顧客收取膠袋徵費，當時發通知書罰款2,000元。至今年三月當局再派員到同一分店突擊巡查，再發現違規事件。環保署執法記錄顯示，A-1 Bakery曾有另外三間分店違規並被罰款，經調查蒐證後向A-1 Bakery提出檢控。<br />\n<br />\n環保署一般對違規商戶處以定額罰款2,000元，重犯或嚴重違規者則會被刑事檢控，被定罪最高可罰款十萬元。當局自全面實施膠袋徵費後曾巡查逾88 000商戶，其間向違規商戶共發出406張定額罰款通知書，並有15宗檢控個案。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170814/57080317\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170814%2F57080317&d=7fTgFZrTg15vyCwIFpNGxE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=6dfecd33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170814%2F57080317&h=02323fe3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170814/57080317</a><br />\n<br />\n幫A1麵包店賺返5000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n環保撚死全家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be73a78efbb7cc28fe4f78af16e321ec2655164","tid":359482,"uid":28031,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:01:42.000Z","msg":"環保撚死全家就最環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7be3aab58c15fe304d2b2c6829641097e81e029","tid":359482,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc28bd16715c31d302bdd65e323354df6e5f830e","tid":359482,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:33:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>環保撚死全家就最環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nX2"},{"pid":"6aff73bd9d46575c7ea067f1536eb80d86d5cb47","tid":359482,"uid":72902,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:40:15.000Z","msg":"搭過佢部廠LIFT後,一世都唔會食A1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">發夢見到成堆小強行黎行去</span></span>"},{"pid":"119896db310e2c808e0a03da3a884888f3b67a5a","tid":359482,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T18:24:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭過佢部廠LIFT後,一世都唔會食A1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">發夢見到成堆小強行黎行去</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64696e245f365810fabde06a1fdfb6ed9ef26fa","tid":359482,"uid":34145,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T00:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭過佢部廠LIFT後,一世都唔會食A1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">發夢見到成堆小強行黎行去</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoj